.TH "nvme_init_get_log_reservation" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_reservation" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_reservation \- Initialize passthru command for Reservation Notification
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_reservation
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_resv_notification_log *log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "log" 12
User address to store the reservation log
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_RESERVATION
